<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddd2cd785-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06" identifier="/us/usc/t12/s4587"><num value="4587">§ 4587.</num><heading> Notice of service</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Any service required or authorized to be made by the Director under this subpart may be made by registered mail or in such other manner reasonably calculated to give actual notice, as the Director may by regulation or otherwise provide.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="iddd2cd786-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06">(<ref href="/us/pl/102/550/tXIII/s1347">Pub. L. 102–550, title XIII, § 1347</ref>, <date date="1992-10-28">Oct. 28, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/3968">106 Stat. 3968</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/110/289/dA/tI/s1130/e/3/D">Pub. L. 110–289, div. A, title I, § 1130(e)(3)(D)</ref>, <date date="2008-07-30">July 30, 2008</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/122/2711">122 Stat. 2711</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
